---
const contactEmail = 'contact@archi-prisma.co.jp';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>Archi-Prisma | Renewal in Progress</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Archi-Prisma のホームページは現在改装中です。お問い合わせはメールにて受け付けています。"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg: #070707;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        --text: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
        --muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
        --accent: #8ff1ff;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html,
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100%;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14), transparent 28%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 82% 16%, rgba(143, 241, 255, 0.18), transparent 18%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #040404 0%, #0c0c0c 48%, #141414 100%);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        padding: 24px;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 1320px;
        min-height: calc(100vh - 48px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .shell {
        display: grid;
        gap: 32px;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(320px, 0.8fr);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--panel);
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.28em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .eyebrow::before {
        content: '';
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(143, 241, 255, 0.7);
      }

      .copy {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .logo-band {
        display: inline-flex;
        max-width: 520px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        padding: 18px 22px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      }

      .logo-band img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.8rem);
        line-height: 0.92;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      p.lead {
        margin: 24px 0 0;
        max-width: 40rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.15rem);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 36px;
      }

      .button,
      .ghost {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 50px;
        padding: 0 24px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition:
          border-color 180ms ease,
          background-color 180ms ease,
          color 180ms ease,
          transform 180ms ease;
      }

      .button {
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #0c0c0c;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: var(--accent);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .ghost {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .ghost:hover {
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .note {
        margin-top: 18px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.48);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 24px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: var(--panel);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .card-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .card-title {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.56);
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.28em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .badge {
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.44);
        font-size: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .logo-surface {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        min-height: 190px;
        padding: 18px;
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: #efefef;
      }

      .logo-surface.warm {
        background: #f4f1eb;
      }

      .logo-surface img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
      }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        body {
          padding: 18px;
        }

        main {
          min-height: calc(100vh - 36px);
        }

        .shell {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="shell">
        <div class="copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Website Renewal in Progress</div>

          <div class="logo-band">
            <img src="/assets/branding/apdw-logo.png" alt="Archi-Prisma Design Works logo" />
          </div>

          <h1>
            ただいま
            <br />
            サイトを改装中です。
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            Archi-Prisma の新しいホームページを準備しています。
            <br />
            公開まで、もう少しだけお待ちください。
          </p>

          <div class="actions">
            <a class="button" href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>お問い合わせはこちら</a>
            <a class="ghost" href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>
          </div>

          <p class="note">
            プロジェクト相談、協業のご連絡、取材のお問い合わせはメールで受け付けています。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cards">
          <article class="card">
            <p class="card-title">Official Logo</p>
            <div class="logo-surface warm">
              <img src="/assets/branding/apdw-logo.png" alt="APDW official logo" />
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <p class="card-title">Development Logo</p>
              <span class="badge">Internal Build</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-surface">
              <img src="/assets/branding/apdw-dev-logo.png" alt="APDW development logo" />
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
